tags: Bindings
title: Mixed Bindings
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A binding can interleave any number of tokens with surrounding text:

```
"title": "{{author}}: {{title}} ({{year}})"
```

For the first book in the [[Profile Description|Profile Description]] example this produces `Frank Herbert: Dune (1965)`.

Single `{` or `}` characters in a binding are literal -- you only need the double form when you want a token.
